snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 Years 1-2 Fighters Edition – Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
The Street Fighter 6 Years 1-2 Fighters Edition will be available on June 5 across all platforms including PlayStation® 5, PlayStation® 4, Xbox Series X|S, PC via Steam, and the new Nintendo Switch™ 2. 

This edition includes characters and stages released from Years 1 & 2 making a total of 26 characters, including their Outfit 1 Colors 3-10, and 20 stages. It's perfect for new players of all skill levels and interests looking to join the fight!

https://www.streetfighter.com/6/contents/y12-fe/
